<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <%= render 'recognition_reward_mailer/styling' %>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    Recognition Reward
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>🏆 Competition Results Are In! 🏆</h2>

    <p>Hello <b><i><%= @user.full_name %></i></b>,</p>

    <p>
      The <b><%= @competition.name %></b> competition has officially concluded!
    </p>

    <p>Thank you for your participation. 🎉</p>

    <p>
      Check the full results on the 
      <a href="<%= "#{@url}/points_log" %>" style="color: #002130; font-weight: bold;">
        Leaderboard
      </a>.
    </p>

    <p>We appreciate your effort and look forward to seeing you in the next challenge!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> GHII Informatics Team. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
